Applysig of MTK recovery features, icluding append signature to the end of image.

WHAT IT DOES?
=============
Applysig appends signature to the end of image.

HOW IT WAS BUILT?
==================
It needs the following library :
1.  libmtdutils
2.  libapplysig
3.  libpartition
4.  libstdc++
5.  libc

All source/dependency modules of this module are already put in
'vendor/mediatek/proprietary/bootable/recovery' and 'alps/bootable/recovery' folder.

HOW TO USE IT?
==============
Provide API for recovery to use it.
all api interface are at (vendor/mediatek/proprietary/protect/bootable/recovery/applysig/applysig.h)

All the source code of this program were written by MediaTek co..
